---

<section class="py-24 lg:py-32 bg-cream relative overflow-hidden" id="about">
  <!-- Decorative elements -->
  <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-stone-light/30 to-transparent"></div>

  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 lg:gap-24 items-center">
      <!-- Left Column: Image/Visual -->
      <div class="relative order-2 lg:order-1">
        <div class="relative">
          <!-- Main image container -->
          <div class="aspect-[4/5] bg-charcoal rounded-2xl overflow-hidden relative">
            <!-- Photo of Todd Frederickson -->
            <img
              src="https://storage.googleapis.com/msgsndr/rUGlMZiYXaprhVgsYQFV/media/692fc3d482f4c57fd9c029bd.png"
              alt="Todd Frederickson, Founder of Singing River AI"
              class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover"
            />

            <!-- Gradient overlay for text readability -->
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-charcoal/90 via-charcoal/20 to-transparent"></div>

            <!-- Content inside the card -->
            <div class="absolute inset-0 flex flex-col justify-end p-8 lg:p-10">
              <!-- Quote or highlight -->
              <div class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-xl p-6 border border-white/10">
                <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-accent mb-4 opacity-50" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path d="M14.017 21v-7.391c0-5.704 3.731-9.57 8.983-10.609l.995 2.151c-2.432.917-3.995 3.638-3.995 5.849h4v10h-9.983zm-14.017 0v-7.391c0-5.704 3.748-9.57 9-10.609l.996 2.151c-2.433.917-3.996 3.638-3.996 5.849h3.983v10h-9.983z" />
                </svg>
                <p class="text-cream/90 font-display text-xl italic leading-relaxed">
                  "AI should be accessible to every business owner, regardless of budget."
                </p>
                <div class="mt-4 pt-4 border-t border-white/10">
                  <p class="text-cream font-medium">Todd Frederickson</p>
                  <p class="text-stone-light text-sm">Founder & AI Advisor</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Floating accent elements -->
          <div class="absolute -top-4 -left-4 w-24 h-24 border-2 border-accent/30 rounded-2xl"></div>
          <div class="absolute -bottom-4 -right-4 w-32 h-32 bg-accent/10 rounded-2xl"></div>

          <!-- Experience badge -->
          <div class="absolute -right-6 top-1/4 bg-white rounded-xl shadow-xl p-4 hidden lg:block">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-accent/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-accent" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M21 13.255A23.931 23.931 0 0112 15c-3.183 0-6.22-.62-9-1.745M16 6V4a2 2 0 00-2-2h-4a2 2 0 00-2 2v2m4 6h.01M5 20h14a2 2 0 002-2V8a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <p class="font-display text-2xl text-charcoal">14+</p>
                <p class="text-xs text-stone">Years in Industry</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Right Column: Content -->
      <div class="order-1 lg:order-2">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-6">
          <div class="w-12 h-px bg-accent"></div>
          <span class="text-sm font-medium text-stone uppercase tracking-widest">About</span>
        </div>

        <h2 class="heading-display text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl mb-8">
          Your trusted <em>AI partner</em>
        </h2>

        <div class="space-y-6 text-stone">
          <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
            I'm Todd Frederickson, founder of Singing River AI with extensive experience in technology and business transformation. My background spans diverse industries, giving me a unique perspective on implementing AI solutions at any scale.
          </p>
          <p class="leading-relaxed">
            I've focused on AI and IT solutions, helping businesses transform their operations through intelligent automation. My mission is to make cutting-edge AI technology accessible to businesses of all sizes.
          </p>
          <p class="leading-relaxed">
            I believe in practical, budget-conscious solutions that deliver real results. No enterprise-level pricing, no unnecessary complexityâ€”just effective AI implementations tailored to your business.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Credentials -->
        <div class="mt-10 pt-10 border-t border-stone-light/30">
          <h3 class="font-medium text-charcoal mb-6">Background & Expertise</h3>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-6">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-accent/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M9.75 17L9 20l-1 1h8l-1-1-.75-3M3 13h18M5 17h14a2 2 0 002-2V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <p class="font-medium text-charcoal">AI Solutions</p>
                <p class="text-sm text-stone">Expert Implementation</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-accent/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <p class="font-medium text-charcoal">Automation</p>
                <p class="text-sm text-stone">Business Process</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-accent/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M12 6.253v13m0-13C10.832 5.477 9.246 5 7.5 5S4.168 5.477 3 6.253v13C4.168 18.477 5.754 18 7.5 18s3.332.477 4.5 1.253m0-13C13.168 5.477 14.754 5 16.5 5c1.747 0 3.332.477 4.5 1.253v13C19.832 18.477 18.247 18 16.5 18c-1.746 0-3.332.477-4.5 1.253" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <p class="font-medium text-charcoal">Training</p>
                <p class="text-sm text-stone">Team Education</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-accent/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <p class="font-medium text-charcoal">SME Focus</p>
                <p class="text-sm text-stone">US Market</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
